/-- **Wiener-Ikehara Tauberian theorem** (PNT+ `WienerIkeharaTheorem''`).
Replaces `PrimeNumberTheoremAnd.Wiener.WienerIkeharaTheorem''`. -/
axiom wiener_ikehara {f : в„• вҶ’ в„қ} {A : в„қ} {G : в„Ӯ вҶ’ в„Ӯ}
    (hpos : 0 вүӨ f)
    (hf : вҲҖ (Пғ' : в„қ), 1 < Пғ' вҶ’ Summable (nterm (fun n => (f n : в„Ӯ)) Пғ'))
    (hG : ContinuousOn G {s | 1 вүӨ s.re})
    (hG' : Set.EqOn G (fun s вҶҰ LSeries (fun n => (f n : в„Ӯ)) s - A / (s - 1)) {s | 1 < s.re}) :
    Filter.Tendsto (fun N => cumsum f N / N) Filter.atTop (nhds A)



