theorem all_primes_over_ri_not_dvd_differentIdeal_of_nonvanishing (в„“ : в„•) (r : Fin в„“ вҶ’ в„•)
    (M : Type) [Field M] [CharZero M] [NumberField M] [IsGalois в„ҡ M]
    (e : (M вүғвӮҗ[в„ҡ] M) вүғ* Multiplicative (Fin в„“ вҶ’ ZMod 3))
